page.title: 07THE MAYOR OF HIGH WYCOMBE
page.content: {MRS BETTY BARRET}WAS UNTIL RECENTLY,THE MAYOR OF{HIGH {WYCOMBE}.SHE HAS LIVED HERE FOR 17 YEARS AND IN VILLAGES NEAR WYCOMBE FOR ALL OF HER LIFE. SHE HAS SEEN MANY CHANGES SUCH AS THE CONSTRUCTION OF THE{OCTAGON {SHOPPING CENTRE}AS WELL AS{HOUSING {PROJECTS.} SHE HAS LOTS OF{CIVIC DUTIES}TO PERFORM SUCH AS GOING TO INSPECT THE TROOP AT THE{WYCOMBE AIR BASE}AND WELCOMING THE MANY{TOURISTS}TO THE TOWN. SHE HAS ENJOYED BEING MAYOR AND HAS PLANS TO HELP THE ELDERLY AND THE DISABLED IN THE AREA.
